title: FATE OF WORLDS: Return to the Ringworld
description:
For decades, the spacefaring species of Known Space have battled over the largest artifact -- and grandest prize -- in the galaxy: the all-but-limitless resources and technology of the Ringworld. But without warning, the Ringworld has vanished, leaving behind three rival war fleets.


The reader is not human, it is TTS. The voice is AT&T Natural Voice NeoSpeech Paul 16 using TextAloud at settings -3 & -3, 24 kbps to minimize file size, quality is the same. I couldn't find any audios of this book so made my own. Not that great, many errors, could be better, but still better than any other audio of this book which I couldn't find.
